comments.author: Kayla B

comments.text:
I rewatched this just now. I remember the first time I watched it was in 
the very beginning of the semester. I'm a fresher studying anbroad, so for 
me the first term was very scary. I remember when the last frame came up 
with the guy saying he never wanted to leave, I couldn't relate. Now on the 
other hand when I'm in my last term before summer, I can relate so much. 
College does something to you. It's called being more mature and growing 
up. Yes I look forward to see all my friends and family back home, but I 
know for sure that I'm gonna miss this place during summer as well. Would 
be fun to take a look at this video in two years from now :)﻿
